{"type":"question","id":4386,"title":"中美關係算總帳？排華潮恐重來？這網友見解犀利","uid":15,"topics":[2003,2036,2037],"contents":"@woodenharp:十年前我开始谈排华，因为读130年前关于排华法案的美国国会辩论后惊恐地发现，当时作为排华理由的各种对华负面刻板印象中很大一部分拿到现在竟然还是成立的。<br>\n比如“中国人在漫长的历史上从未建立进行过有效的自我管理”、“中国人不珍视公民权，会毫不犹豫把它卖掉”，还有其它更难听的。<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7Ioqd3WkAEBSDY?format=png&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7Ioqd3WkAEBSDY?format=png&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7Ioqd3WkAEBSDY?format=png&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7IotMhWsAA32De?format=png&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7IotMhWsAA32De?format=png&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7IotMhWsAA32De?format=png&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7Io0k_X4AE_zoy?format=png&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7Io0k_X4AE_zoy?format=png&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7Io0k_X4AE_zoy?format=png&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7Io13UW4AA3r9P?format=png&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7Io13UW4AA3r9P?format=png&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D7Io13UW4AA3r9P?format=png&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-05-22","agreeCount":-1,"discussionCount":0}